data.description: Discover your dream home in Eastover, NC—a captivating 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2-story home with 2900sf. Outside, enjoy an inviting front porch and a spacious backyard. Inside features a cozy fireplace, open-ish kitchen, and a versatile room for an office or guest bedroom. Upstairs, a luxurious master suite, 2 additional bedrooms, and large bonus room that doubles as a 4th bedroom. No carpet downstairs, both HVACs replaced in 2017, (with extended warranties & include electronic filtration systems) 2 car garage and ample storage add to the allure. Located conveniently near Fayetteville, Fort Liberty, and great schools. Don't miss out—schedule a showing today!
